trans-unit.source: Represents a database column that is used by Dynamic Data.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en databasekolonne som brukes i dynamiske Data.

trans-unit.source: In ASP.NET Dynamic Data applications, the MetaColumn class represents a database field.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MetaColumn representerer en databasefeltet i dynamiske Data for ASP.NET-applikasjoner.

trans-unit.source: The MetaColumn class lets you retrieve information about the data field such as type and metadata information.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MetaColumn kan du hente informasjon om data-feltet for eksempel type og metadata.

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve the table that the data field belongs to by using the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.Table%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hente tabellen datafeltet hører til ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.Table%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.Table%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also retrieve the data model by using the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.Model%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også hente datamodellen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.Model%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.Model%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.StringLengthAttribute> attribute is not applied to the data field, the MaxLength property uses the database type to retrieve the maximum length allowed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.StringLengthAttribute>attributtet brukes ikke til datafelt, egenskapen MaxLength bruker databasetypen ikke hente den maksimale tillatte lengden.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.StringLengthAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The maximum length of data that can be stored in the data field.
trans-unit.target: Den maksimale lengden på data som kan lagres i data-feltet.

trans-unit.source: Clears cached column metadata.
trans-unit.target: Tømmer bufrede kolonnemetadata.

trans-unit.source: The column metadata is information that is derived from attributes and that is cached for performance.
trans-unit.target: Metadataene som kolonnen er informasjon som er avledet fra attributter, og som er hurtigbufret for ytelse.

trans-unit.source: Calling this method clears the metadata cache for this column.
trans-unit.target: Kaller denne metoden tømmes metadatabufferen for denne kolonnen.

trans-unit.source: The metadata cache is rebuilt the next time any information that is derived from metadata is requested.
trans-unit.target: Metadatabufferen bygges på nytt neste gang informasjon som er avledet fra metadata forespørres.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the data field should be displayed.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om data-feltet skal vises.

trans-unit.source: The Scaffold property indicates whether a data field should be displayed when it is automatically generated by ASP.NET Dynamic Data.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Scaffold angir om et datafelt skal vises når genereres automatisk av ASP.NET dynamiske Data.

trans-unit.source: This property verifies if a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute> attribute is applied to the data field and returns the value of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute.Scaffold%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kontrollerer om en <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute>attributtet brukes til data-feltet, og returnerer verdien for den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute.Scaffold%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute.Scaffold%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute> attribute is not applied to the data field, Dynamic Data uses the following rules to determine whether to display the column: - If a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.UIHintAttribute> attribute is applied to the data field, the data field is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute>attributtet brukes ikke til datafelt, dynamiske Data bruker følgende regler om skal vise kolonnen: – Hvis en <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.UIHintAttribute>attributtet brukes til datafelt, datafeltet vises.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.UIHintAttribute> </xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ScaffoldColumnAttribute>

trans-unit.source: This rule overrides all the other rules.
trans-unit.target: Denne regelen overstyrer alle andre regler.

trans-unit.source: - If the value of the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsForeignKeyComponent%2A> property is `true`, the data field is not displayed.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsForeignKeyComponent%2A>egenskapen `true`, vises ikke datafeltet.</xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsForeignKeyComponent%2A>

trans-unit.source: This occurs because Dynamic Data handles foreign-key fields in a different way and will not typically display the foreign-key field value.
trans-unit.target: Dette skjer fordi dynamiske Data behandler sekundærnøkkel felt i en annen måte og vises ikke vanligvis sekundærnøkkel feltverdien.

trans-unit.source: - If the value of the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsGenerated%2A> property is `true`, the data field is not displayed.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsGenerated%2A>egenskapen `true`, vises ikke datafeltet.</xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsGenerated%2A>

trans-unit.source: Typically fields that are automatically generated in the database do not contain relevant information.
trans-unit.target: Felt som genereres automatisk i databasen inneholder vanligvis ikke relevant informasjon.

trans-unit.source: Make sure that you apply the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.UIHintAttribute> attribute to the data field, if the data field must be displayed.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller at du bruker den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.UIHintAttribute>attributt til datafeltet Hvis data-feltet må vises.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.UIHintAttribute>

trans-unit.source: - If the value of the <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsCustomProperty%2A> property is `true`, the data field is not displayed.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsCustomProperty%2A>egenskapen `true`, vises ikke datafeltet.</xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaColumn.IsCustomProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the data field should be displayed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis data-feltet skal vises; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
